<h2>Favors</h2>

<h3>Andre&aacute; Alford wedding site</h3>

<p>Frustrated with the commercial wedding site she was using, my friend Andy asked me to build a website for her April 9, 2005 wedding.</p>

<p>The couple didn't really have a decent photo of themselves, so I suggested that they head to an Amy's Ice Cream location and spend a few dollars goofing around in the photo booth. I took those photos and, with a little help from Photoshop, turned them into the main design element for the site.</p>

<p>I got the idea for using a photo booth from the back cover of Duran Duran's second self-titled album, better known as <em>The Wedding Album</em>.</p>

<p>The site is no longer running on account that the marriage was a mistake.</p>

